{"_id":"uxzMha0FT7OdOnmJ","name":"Fire Bomb","type":"curio","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/bomb-fuse-red-black.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to make a ranged special attack using your DEX against a target within 30 feet of you. On a hit, you deal **2d6 fire damage** to the target. Alternatively, you may instead make a Wreck an Object check against the target and add \\+2 to the total.\n\nRegardless if the check succeeds or fails, you also designate a 10 foot radius sphere originating from the target. The target and all creatures and objects in the area are dealt an additional **1d8 fire damage**.","rarity":"Common","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"30","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Bomb","flavor":"Light them up.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":1000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"cZJuEBKqfScFeoEf","name":"Stormcaller Dart","type":"curio","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/dart-feathered.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to make a ranged special attack using your DEX against a target within 30 feet of you. On a hit, you deal **4d6 lightning damage** to the target. Alternatively, you may instead make a Wreck an Object check against the target and add \\+4 to the total.\n\nRegardless if the check succeeds or fails, you also designate a 10 foot radius, 60 foot tall cylinder originating from the target. The target and all creatures and objects in the area are dealt an additional **2d8 lightning damage**. Affected creatures lose a reaction if they had one.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Bomb","flavor":"Electric filaments trail the trajectory as bolts of lightning hone in on the target.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":2000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"f7BDtgt6iyCZqkWi","name":"Frost Snare","type":"curio","img":"icons/weapons/thrown/bomb-fuse-blue.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to make a ranged special attack using your DEX against a target within 30 feet of you. On a hit, you deal **6d6 cold damage** to the target. Alternatively, you may instead make a Wreck an Object check against the target and add \\+6 to the total.\n\nRegardless if the check succeeds or fails, you also designate a 10 foot radius sphere originating from the target. The target and all creatures and objects in the area are dealt an additional **3d8 cold damage** and become stuck with the **Recoverable** condition trait, allowing an action to end the effect.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Bomb","flavor":"Shimmering icicles weave into frozen netting as they burst out of the bomb.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":3000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Sz90HSUNaFo5BzFN","name":"Caustic Flask","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-conical-corked-labeled-skull-poison-green.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to make a ranged special attack using your DEX against a target within 30 feet of you. On a hit, you deal **8d6 acid damage** to the target. Alternatively, you may instead make a Wreck an Object check against the target and add \\+8 to the total.\n\nRegardless if the check succeeds or fails, you also designate a 10 foot radius sphere originating from the target. The target and all creatures and objects in the area are dealt an additional **4d8 acid damage**. Affected creatures cease to have any effect that grants them their Half Guard AC or their Full Guard AC.","rarity":"Legendary","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"60","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Bomb","flavor":"With how much it steams and bubbles inside, there is no question about how it is meant to be used.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":4000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"96cHpBPvVurmtwtp","name":"Acidic Smear","type":"curio","img":"icons/skills/melee/blade-tip-acid-poison-green.webp","system":{"description":"This item can exist at multiple rarities. The Common/Uncommon/Rare/Legendary variants of this item have a crafting threshold score of 30/40/50/60 respectively, and other statistics shown below use this same notation.\n\nAs a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon you are holding for the next 10 minutes. A weapon may not be coated by more than one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. Weapon attack hits made with a weapon coated by this item gain the following benefits:\n\n* All of the damage dealt is converted to **acid damage**.\n\n* The attack's damage roll is increased by **1d6/2d6/3d6/4d6 damage**.\n\n* Damage taken reduction from DBs is halved against damage dealt by the attack.","rarity":"Varies","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"Varies","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Oil","flavor":"Dripping acid sizzles as it splatters on the ground while you prepare a deadly offensive.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":5000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"MztUovxSWhwBOQqy","name":"Condensed Gloom","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/flask-corked-purple-glow.webp","system":{"description":"This item can exist at multiple rarities. The Common/Uncommon/Rare/Legendary variants of this item have a crafting threshold score of 30/40/50/60 respectively, and other statistics shown below use this same notation.\n\nAs a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon you are holding for the next 10 minutes. A weapon may not be coated by more than one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. Weapon attack hits made with a weapon coated by this item gain the following benefits:\n\n* All of the damage dealt is converted to **necrotic damage**.\n\n* The attack's damage roll is increased by **1d6/2d6/3d6/4d6 damage**.\n\n* Damage taken reduction from DBs is halved against damage dealt by the attack.","rarity":"Varies","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"Varies","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Oil","flavor":"A thick, droopy gloom coating your weapon, drawing in life and moisture with each passing second.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":6000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
