{"_id":"2X2HY5LtlSfFfcnG","name":"Flippergulp","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-flask-corked-cyan.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next long rest:\n\n* **Amphibious.** You are able to breathe underwater.\n\n* **Webbed Toes.** You gain advanced Swimming mobility.\n\n* **Piscine Features.** While suffering from potion toxicity, you gain visible scales and cannot blink.","rarity":"Common","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"30","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"This immiscible solution separates into air on the bottom and liquid on top. Shaking before drinking ensures you only get the best parts of being a fish.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":19000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
