{"_id":"8SSikTsFNGyOxGPv","name":"Limb Libation","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-ornate-bat-teal.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Elongation.** Your Reach is increased by 5 feet.\n\n* **Constriction.** Whenever you succeed on a Grapple or Pin check, you deal **2d4 bludgeoning damage** to the target of the action.\n\n* **Flammable.** While suffering from potion toxicity, **fire damage** dealt to you is doubled and sets you ablaze.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"The charred eye of a young kraken sizzles at the bottom of the flask, trapped in its final moments of agony.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":25000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nTkD6cVfX9Up9V44","name":"Slime Salve","type":"curio","img":"icons/commodities/materials/slime-green.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Toxic Skin.** When you are hit with a melee attack, you deal **5 acid damage** or **5 poison damage** to the attacker.\n\n* **Autoimmune.** You gain DB 5 against **acid** and **poison damage**.\n\n* **Slippery.** While suffering from potion toxicity, using prone's **Recoverable** trait requires an additional action.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"An almost chalky texture, but with a mossy flavor. This hazardous sludge invites only the daring.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":26000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"f3ff812qHGA95ve8","name":"Perspicacity Drop","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/vial-cork-blue.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Clarity.** You gain advantage on **Quick-Wits** and **Will** saving throws.\n\n* **Hyper-autoawareness.** While suffering from potion toxicity, ST regained from burning a Resolve is halved.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"This translucent, colorless liquid rotates more slowly than the bottle when jostled. When poured, its faceted inner structure gives way to a crisp finish.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":27000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"NUH6ie4vg3cOahnp","name":"Bladeward Brew","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-faceted-corked-blue.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Stone Skin.** You may act as if you are wearing Stock Armor and without needing to meet its STR requirement\n\n* **Calcified.** You gain DB 15 against **physical damage**.\n\n* **Gout.** While suffering from potion toxicity, when your DB from this potion breaks, you take **5 injuring piercing damage**.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"An azure solution that settles into a splintery precipitate. Shake before drinking.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":28000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yAAs9taUiW5wqVHv","name":"Lifting Drink","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/drinks/alcohol-spirits-bottle-blue.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Upper.** You gain basic Hovering mobility.\n\n* **Downer.** While suffering from potion toxicity, you incur disadvantage on STR and DEX checks.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"Drunk upside-down, the rising liquid fills your sinuses with a cooling burn.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":29000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"CYHTxn6PGJlFatCK","name":"Lightning Stim","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/flask-corked-yellow-glow.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Overclock.** All attack checks you make gain advantage.\n\n* **Overdrive.** Whenever you hit a creature or object with an attack twice within a single turn, you add **6d6 lightning damage** to the damage roll of the second attack.\n\n* **Meltdown.** While suffering from potion toxicity, half the damage you deal with **Overdrive** is also dealt to you.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"Electric anticipation bubbles within this concentrated shot of energy.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":30000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hqAqKoKyXzt3Swfv","name":"Photonic Flask","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-round-label-cork-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Lightweight.** Your Speed is doubled.\n\n* **Cardio.** At the end of each of your turns, you **regain ST** equal to half the amount of feet you traveled in that turn.\n\n* **Endorphin Glow.** While suffering from potion toxicity, you cannot benefit from being invisible.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"Vaporized sunlight scatters out of the opaque bottle as it is uncorked, disappearing in a flash if not immediately consumed.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":31000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"bxIgowAeahIQT8MD","name":"Rotgut","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/flask-ornate-skull-green.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Bloating.** As a free action once per turn, when you are dealt damage, you may deal **12 necrotic damage** to all creatures and objects within 10 feet of you.\n\n* **Engorged.** You and other creatures within 10 feet of you are slowed and the damage they deal to you is halved.\n\n* **Flatulence.** While suffering from potion toxicity, you have disadvantage on CHA checks.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"Putrid ooze permeates through the glass, grows on its surface, and emits a sweet stench.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":32000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eY9ouXaZz7CFYQwq","name":"Spirits of Severance","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/drinks/alcohol-jar-spirits-gray.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Dematerialization.** Attack checks against you incur disadvantage.\n\n* **Phase Shift.** At the end of your turn, you may choose to become *phased out* until the start of your next turn. While phased out, you are unable to affect other subjects and cannot be affected by subjects other than yourself.\n\n* **Dissociation.** While suffering from potion toxicity, instead of choosing whether to use **Phase Shift** at the end of your turn, you make a DC 11 flat check and phase out on a failure.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"The weight within the bottle sporadically shifts as parts of the solution phase in and out of the physical realm.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":33000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"AyrZUurgaxnonynD","name":"Divinity Dram","type":"curio","img":"icons/magic/holy/chalice-glowing-gold.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Heavenly.** You gain a \\+5 bonus to all attack and combat checks.\n\n* **Euphoria.** While suffering from potion toxicity, when you take damage, you become pacified until the end of your next turn.","rarity":"Legendary","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"60","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"Made from rare, celestial flowers, this mother-of-pearl solution contains gold flakes that drift in sacred spirals.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":34000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"ePhHMJCpgkpxNpX6","name":"Misfortune Inoculation","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-bottle-labeled-medicine-capped-red-black.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Critical Immunity.** Critical hits scored against you instead count as normal hits.\n\n* **Metal Macrophages.** When an attack made against you misses, you gain your Full Guard AC until the start of your next turn.\n\n* **Adverse Equilibrium.** While suffering from potion toxicity, critical hits you score instead count as a normal hit.","rarity":"Legendary","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"60","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"The sour taste of disappointment lingers on your palate, preparing your body to defend against the worst of fates.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":35000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"2CvjGFICM7PFvFuX","name":"Transparency Draft","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-bulb-empty-glass.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to gain the following potion effects until the end of your next rest:\n\n* **Translucent.** You are invisible.\n\n* **Photofriction.** While suffering from potion toxicity, you are slowed.","rarity":"Legendary","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"60","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Potion","flavor":"A fluid so clear that the bottom of the flask vanishes before your eyes.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":36000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"b1oic1RZeadAUfV8","name":"Poultice","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-bottle-corked-white.webp","system":{"description":"This item can exist at multiple rarities. The Common/Uncommon/Rare/Legendary variants of this item have a crafting threshold score of 30/40/50/60 respectively, and other statistics shown below use this same notation.\n\nYou may expend this item by administering it to a target creature within your Reach either as a Use Item action or over the course of one minute. Depending on the time taken, this item grants different benefits to the target:\n\n* **As a Use Item action,** the target **regains 20/40/60/80 ST**.\n\n* **Over one minute,** the target **heals 5/10/15/20 HP**.","rarity":"Varies","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"Varies","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Remedy","flavor":"Though it takes time to set, a quick solution can often work just as well.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":37000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"8diiWY7kWxg6nNDF","name":"Antidote","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-bottle-corked-labeled-green.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item by administering it to a target creature within your Reach, cleansing the target of the disoriented and poisoned conditions.","rarity":"Common","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"30","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Remedy","flavor":"A fermented shot of wellness for the ailing.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":38000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"J183LK7DIQ8O9emz","name":"Nightmare Solvent","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-round-flask-fumes-purple.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item by administering it to a target creature within your Reach, cleansing the target of the disoriented and frightened conditions.","rarity":"Common","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"30","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Remedy","flavor":"Sloshing within the bizarre putty are boundless imaginations. All your fears and confusions just melt away.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":39000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"LoXUdpT2ezYz7lrb","name":"Slip Grease","type":"curio","img":"icons/commodities/materials/slime-thick-blue.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item by administering it to a target creature within your Reach, removing the grappled, stuck, and restrained conditions from the target.","rarity":"Common","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"30","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Remedy","flavor":"If only the lid would stay on.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":40000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yYqkPyBoQRuQAMH0","name":"Ecliptic Elixir","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-conical-corked-purple.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item by administering it to a target creature within your Reach, cleansing the target of the poisoned and polymorphed conditions.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Remedy","flavor":"Twinkling starlets bespeckle the solution as floating dust. A gaping void is suspended in the liquid, obscuring the wondrous display behind it.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":41000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"BLUpL4m4R54PS6cM","name":"Liquid Courage","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/drinks/alcohol-beer-mug-yellow.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item by administering it to a target creature within your Reach, cleansing the target of the frightened and incapacitated conditions.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Remedy","flavor":"It's probably just whiskey, but half the effect comes from believing in it.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":42000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1b9jtwKKWD1KSls8","name":"Distilled Clarity","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-round-empty-glass.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item by administering it to a target creature within your Reach, cleansing the target of the disoriented and stunned conditions.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Remedy","flavor":"An aftertaste that separates out the individual flavors of what came before. The pieces of the puzzle have been slotted into place.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":43000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"AUA5JzKQ5w97kKDP","name":"Panacea","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-bottle-corked-fancy-orange.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item by administering it to a target creature within your Reach, cleansing the target of all negative conditions.","rarity":"Legendary","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"60","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Remedy","flavor":"A kaleidoscopic concoction that shifts in color and texture when in proximity of the patient. It truly cures all.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":44000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"nDbsST85YnTgy6no","name":"Deadly Poison","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-bottle-skull-label-poison-teal.webp","system":{"description":"This item can exist at multiple rarities. The Common/Uncommon/Rare/Legendary variants of this item have a crafting threshold score of 30/40/50/60 respectively, and other statistics shown below use this same notation.\n\nAs a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon or three pieces of ammunition you are holding until the end of your next long rest. An item may only be coated by one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. The type of item you coat determines when the toxin's effect is applied:\n\n* **Ammunition.** When you make a ranged weapon attack with the coated ammunition, the ammunition is expended and the below effect is applied if the attack hits.\n\n* **Weapon.** On the first time you hit with a melee weapon attack using the coated weapon, the below effect is applied.\n\nWhen this toxin is applied to a creature, the target is dealt **2d8/4d8/6d8/8d8 poison damage**.","rarity":"Varies","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"Varies","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Toxin","flavor":"It's not about sending a message - it's about ensuring there is no receiver.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":45000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"EwRzFK0tkjdW11FG","name":"Deadly Serum","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-conical-fumes-green.webp","system":{"description":"This item can exist at multiple rarities. The Common/Uncommon/Rare/Legendary variants of this item have a crafting threshold score of 30/40/50/60 respectively, and other statistics shown below use this same notation.\n\nAs a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon or three pieces of ammunition you are holding until the end of your next long rest. An item may only be coated by one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. The type of item you coat determines when the toxin's effect is applied:\n\n* **Ammunition.** When you make a ranged weapon attack with the coated ammunition, the ammunition is expended and the below effect is applied if the attack hits.\n\n* **Weapon.** On the first time you hit with a melee weapon attack using the coated weapon, the below effect is applied.\n\nWhen this toxin is applied to a creature, the target is dealt **2d8/4d8/6d8/8d8 psychic damage**.","rarity":"Varies","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"Varies","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Toxin","flavor":"A variant extract concocted for directed mental attacks.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":46000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uTRB1R1ZNfEYAko0","name":"Sickening Poison","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-jar-corked-labeled-poison-skull-green.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon or three pieces of ammunition you are holding until the end of your next long rest. An item may only be coated by one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. The type of item you coat determines when the toxin's effect is applied:\n\n* **Ammunition.** When you make a ranged weapon attack with the coated ammunition, the ammunition is expended and the below effect is applied if the attack hits.\n\n* **Weapon.** On the first time you hit with a melee weapon attack using the coated weapon, the below effect is applied.\n\nWhen this toxin is applied to a creature, the target is poisoned. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they must make a DC 14 **Fortitude** saving throw, ending the effect on a success.","rarity":"Common","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"30","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Toxin","flavor":"Catching even a whiff of the foul stench can make you feel queasy.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":47000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"eyKDoABsxfRVcl7P","name":"Twisted Serum","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/bottle-round-label-cork-purple.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon or three pieces of ammunition you are holding until the end of your next long rest. An item may only be coated by one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. The type of item you coat determines when the toxin's effect is applied:\n\n* **Ammunition.** When you make a ranged weapon attack with the coated ammunition, the ammunition is expended and the below effect is applied if the attack hits.\n\n* **Weapon.** On the first time you hit with a melee weapon attack using the coated weapon, the below effect is applied.\n\nWhen this toxin is applied to a creature, the target is disoriented. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they must make a DC 14 **Quick-Wits** saving throw, ending the effect on a success.","rarity":"Common","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"30","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Toxin","flavor":"A frothy fluid that never seems to come to rest. Staring into it for too long can induce a minor loss of balance.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":48000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"uvQppgtCdjWywdar","name":"Repulsive Serum","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/conical-ornate-purple.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon or three pieces of ammunition you are holding until the end of your next long rest. An item may only be coated by one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. The type of item you coat determines when the toxin's effect is applied:\n\n* **Ammunition.** When you make a ranged weapon attack with the coated ammunition, the ammunition is expended and the below effect is applied if the attack hits.\n\n* **Weapon.** On the first time you hit with a melee weapon attack using the coated weapon, the below effect is applied.\n\nWhen this toxin is applied to a creature, the target is frightened of the attacker. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they must make a DC 17 **Courage** saving throw, ending the effect on a success.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Toxin","flavor":"A refined distillation of pure terror.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":49000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"zNWGWIOl95xqPSA0","name":"Tranquil Poison","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/vial-cork-green.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon or three pieces of ammunition you are holding until the end of your next long rest. An item may only be coated by one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. The type of item you coat determines when the toxin's effect is applied:\n\n* **Ammunition.** When you make a ranged weapon attack with the coated ammunition, the ammunition is expended and the below effect is applied if the attack hits.\n\n* **Weapon.** On the first time you hit with a melee weapon attack using the coated weapon, the below effect is applied.\n\nWhen this toxin is applied to a creature, the target falls unconscious if they have no Resolve remaining.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Toxin","flavor":"A glossy, translucent solution favored for silent takedowns.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":50000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"hdlja9Oh1BX7qXHk","name":"Dazing Poison","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/vial-cork-red.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon or three pieces of ammunition you are holding until the end of your next long rest. An item may only be coated by one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. The type of item you coat determines when the toxin's effect is applied:\n\n* **Ammunition.** When you make a ranged weapon attack with the coated ammunition, the ammunition is expended and the below effect is applied if the attack hits.\n\n* **Weapon.** On the first time you hit with a melee weapon attack using the coated weapon, the below effect is applied.\n\nWhen this toxin is applied to a creature, the target is incapacitated. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they must make a DC 20 **Fortitude** saving throw, ending the effect on a success.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Toxin","flavor":"The scarlet hue and complete sense of numbness are both signatures of this toxin.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":51000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Fun7Z92EiN6y8QVS","name":"Newtative Serum","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-flask-corked-green.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon or three pieces of ammunition you are holding until the end of your next long rest. An item may only be coated by one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. The type of item you coat determines when the toxin's effect is applied:\n\n* **Ammunition.** When you make a ranged weapon attack with the coated ammunition, the ammunition is expended and the below effect is applied if the attack hits.\n* **Weapon.** On the first time you hit with a melee weapon attack using the coated weapon, the below effect is applied.\n\nWhen this toxin is applied to a creature, the target must make a DC 20 **Fortitude** saving throw. On a failure, the target is polymorphed into a newt, a Tier 0 beast creature. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they may retry the saving throw, ending the effect on a success.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Toxin","flavor":"They might get better.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":52000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"J3nWpz0UQAhUXIEU","name":"Horror Serum","type":"curio","img":"icons/commodities/materials/slime-purple.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon or three pieces of ammunition you are holding until the end of your next long rest. An item may only be coated by one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. The type of item you coat determines when the toxin's effect is applied:\n\n* **Ammunition.** When you make a ranged weapon attack with the coated ammunition, the ammunition is expended and the below effect is applied if the attack hits.\n\n* **Weapon.** On the first time you hit with a melee weapon attack using the coated weapon, the below effect is applied.\n\nWhen this toxin is applied to a creature, the target is affected by the following:\n\n* **Fear.** The target is frightened of every creature.\n\n* **Hopelessness.** This frightened condition has the **No Spellcasting** condition trait, preventing the affected creature from casting spells.\n\n* **Panic.** The target, if they were concentrating on a spell effect, loses concentration.\n\n* **Psychosomatic Pain.** While frightened, melee attacks that hit the creature automatically score a critical hit. All damage dealt by these attacks is converted to **psychic damage**.\n\nAt the end of an affected creature's turn, they must make a DC 23 **Courage** saving throw, ending the effect on a success.","rarity":"Legendary","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"60","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Toxin","flavor":"Appearing different to each observer, the heinous slime reflects your own fears with cruel precision.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":53000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"oci8SkP2hkjwXNTG","name":"Stunning Poison","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/flask-corked-green.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you may expend this item to *coat* a weapon or three pieces of ammunition you are holding until the end of your next long rest. An item may only be coated by one oil or toxin consumable item at a time. The type of item you coat determines when the toxin's effect is applied:\n\n* **Ammunition.** When you make a ranged weapon attack with the coated ammunition, the ammunition is expended and the below effect is applied if the attack hits.\n\n* **Weapon.** On the first time you hit with a melee weapon attack using the coated weapon, the below effect is applied.\n\nWhen this toxin is applied to a creature, the target is stunned. At the end of an affected creature's turn, they must make a DC 23 **Fortitude** saving throw, ending the effect on a success.\n\n# **List of Artisan Items**","rarity":"Legendary","discipline":"Alchemist","craftingThresholdScore":"60","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Consumable","subType":"Toxin","flavor":"A potent venom employed by dangerous monsters to stun their prey.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":54000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"M5caHjCATCxlLvqn","name":"Bountiful Vessel","type":"curio","img":"icons/commodities/materials/bowl-liquid-white.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action, you dispense a specific liquid from the list below at a maximum rate of 2 gallons per minute: any alcoholic beverage, coffee, tea, mayonnaise, oil, fresh or salt water, or vinegar.","rarity":"Common","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"30","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"This vessel can be found in many aesthetic designs, but no self-respecting chef in a magical world is without one.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":55000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
