{"_id":"MeKkww7Xyb172RVZ","name":"Paradoxical Pouch","type":"curio","img":"icons/containers/bags/pouch-leather-brown-green.webp","system":{"description":"This Tiny container holds within it an extra-dimensional space that is up to 64 cubic feet in volume. When you stow an object, you may instead put it in the container, but you must take a Use Item action to retrieve an item from the container. All objects stowed in the container spill out if the container is destroyed.\n\nA creature occupying the container begins asphyxiating (as described by the Swimming mobility) after 6 hours spent inside.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"It's just false bottoms all the way down.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":63000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"JX6gpBWsO6wm0kvH","name":"Potion Gun","type":"curio","img":"icons/weapons/guns/gun-pistol-flintlock-metal.webp","system":{"description":"As an object interaction, you may *load* a potion or remedy stowed on you into this item. Use a Use Item action, you may expend the loaded item to apply its effects to a target creature within 30 feet of you.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"object interaction","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"The exact solution to your problem, delivered by the fastest and most cathartic method.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":64000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"yjtpXqaoEJmvlzXx","name":"Prying Phial","type":"curio","img":"icons/consumables/potions/potion-flask-corked-tied-necklace-teal.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action once per rest, you may cast **Tracker Sense** at 1st Circle using your INT, WIS, or CHA as your spellcasting modifier.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"Wisps of twinkling smoke waft out of the stopper, drifting towards an adversary of your naming.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":65000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
