{"_id":"RwCLzVYTvuEtcFdQ","name":"Asynchronic Stopwatch","type":"curio","img":"icons/magic/time/clock-stopwatch-white-blue.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action once per rest, you may cast **Riftwalk** at 2nd Circle using your INT, WIS, or CHA as your spellcasting modifier with the following heightening enhancement automatically chosen:\n\n* You may bring a target willing creature within your Reach with you, teleporting them with you.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"The whir of the timepiece's machinery is your only motion in the ever-moving universe, as you watch it drift by for a moment, only to snap back into reality a few feet away.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":69000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"Ak2yg96WocNu14Kr","name":"Dome-icile","type":"curio","img":"icons/magic/defensive/barrier-shield-dome-blue-purple.webp","system":{"description":"Once per rest, you may cast **Warding Circle** at 1st Circle using your INT, WIS, or CHA as your spellcasting modifier.\n\nWhen you use this item to cast **Warding Circle**, the designated area is instead a 15 foot radius sphere, it does not have its **Permanence** trait, and you may designate all creature type tags then choose any number of creatures to be unaffected by the spell effect.","rarity":"Uncommon","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"40","actionType":"Passive","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"This tiny wooden bowl, carved with runes, can expand to form a dome of force capable of providing a comfortable and safe resting area for you and your companions.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":70000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"9Be79NgY8eRjUmwY","name":"Forgotten Effigy","type":"curio","img":"icons/commodities/treasure/figurine-idol.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action once per rest, you may cast **Cloak** at 2nd Circle using your INT, WIS, or CHA as your spellcasting modifier with the following heightening enhancement automatically chosen:\n\n* You may choose for the casting of this spell to be imperceptible.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"An enigmatic figurine whose ghostly image appears to beckon you forward, forever cursed to lead its handlers down paths untrodden and out of sight.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":71000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"czBLgwGtBiaUtBgX","name":"Living Chainmail","type":"curio","img":"icons/commodities/metal/mail-chain-steel.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action once per rest, you may cast either **Defender Drone** or **Fortify** at 1st Circle using your INT, WIS, or CHA as your spellcasting modifier.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"A semi-sentient web of metal threads crackling and roiling with nervous energy, capable of fending off attackers with electric flicks if left to its own devices or reinforcing a structure if properly coaxed.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":72000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"qXiLnL2T8cyXXWaF","name":"Mirror of Aspiration","type":"curio","img":"icons/sundries/survival/mirror-plain.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action once per rest, you may cast **Disguise** at 2nd Circle using your INT, WIS, or CHA as your spellcasting modifier with the following heightening enhancement automatically chosen:\n\n* An affected creature may take an action to change their appearance again to a new one of their choosing.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"A window of pale silver that casts its onlookers with the trappings of their ever-shifting desires.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":73000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"1M1PKRmXZCjIUXQh","name":"Verdant Switch","type":"curio","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-forest-green.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action once per rest, you may cast **Climbing Vine** at 2nd Circle using your INT, WIS, or CHA as your spellcasting modifier with the following heightening enhancement automatically chosen:\n\n* The climbing vine's Toughness becomes 15\\.","rarity":"Rare","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"50","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"A wooden staff that never lost its spark of life, fostering vibrant microcosms within the gnarls and knots of the ancient wood.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":74000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
{"_id":"dzzwFGd1rKcIMLlw","name":"Apogeic Tether","type":"curio","img":"icons/weapons/staves/staff-engraved-wood.webp","system":{"description":"As a Use Item action once per rest, you may cast **Leyline Jaunt** at 4th Circle using your INT, WIS, or CHA as your spellcasting modifier.","rarity":"Legendary","discipline":"Artisan","craftingThresholdScore":"60","actionType":"Use Item action","mainType":"Gadget","subType":"","flavor":"A divergent hook catching the convergent threads of the universe, allowing you to zip towards its vertex at nauseating speeds.","quantity":1,"weight":0},"effects":[],"folder":null,"sort":75000,"ownership":{"default":0},"permission":{"default":0},"flags":{}}
